<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Inner Compass — Ma'at Rising</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700&family=Cinzel:wght@400;600&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
:root{--gold:#C9A84C;--gold-light:#E8C97A;--gold-dim:#7a6020;--deep:#0a0705;--dark:#110e08;--panel:#1a1509;--panel2:#221c0d;--text:#f0e6c8;--text-dim:#a89060;--teal:#3AAFA9;--teal-dark:#1d7874;--white:#fff8ec;--border:rgba(201,168,76,0.25);--glow:0 0 24px rgba(201,168,76,0.18);}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{background:var(--deep);color:var(--text);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;}
#stars{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;}
.star{position:absolute;background:#fff;border-radius:50%;animation:twinkle var(--d,3s) ease-in-out infinite alternate;}
@keyframes twinkle{from{opacity:.1;}to{opacity:.8;}}
.screen{display:none;position:relative;z-index:1;min-height:100vh;}
.screen.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
#onboarding{align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%,#2a1f00 0%,#0a0705 70%);}
.onboard-box{max-width:520px;width:90%;text-align:center;padding:3rem 2.5rem;background:rgba(26,21,9,0.85);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;box-shadow:var(--glow);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);animation:fadeUp .8s ease both;}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.ankh{font-size:3.5rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;animation:pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{text-shadow:0 0 20px var(--gold);}50%{text-shadow:0 0 50px var(--gold-light);}}
.brand-title{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--gold);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:.3rem;}
.brand-sub{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:1.2rem 0;}
.step{display:none;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both;}
.step.visible{display:block;}
.step-label{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--gold-dim);margin-bottom:.8rem;}
.step h2{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold-light);margin-bottom:.7rem;}
.step p{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.ob-input{width:100%;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;outline:none;transition:border .3s;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.ob-input:focus{border-color:var(--gold);}
.ob-btn{display:inline-block;padding:.75rem 2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-dim));color:var(--deep);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);}
.ob-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);}
.dot-row{display:flex;gap:.5rem;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--panel2);transition:background .3s;}
.dot.active{background:var(--gold);}
#app{flex-direction:column;}
.top-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:.9rem 1.4rem;background:rgba(17,14,8,0.95);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.top-title{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--gold);}
.greeting-bar{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;}
.tab-nav{display:flex;overflow-x:auto;background:var(--panel);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);scrollbar-width:none;}
.tab-nav::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
.tab-btn{flex-shrink:0;padding:.7rem 1.1rem;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--text-dim);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:all .25s;white-space:nowrap;}
.tab-btn.active{color:var(--gold);border-bottom-color:var(--gold);}
.tab-content{display:none;flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:1.2rem;}
.tab-content.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.temple-header{text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0 1rem;}
.temple-header .ankh-sm{font-size:2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:.4rem;}
.temple-header h1{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.2rem;}
.temple-header p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;letter-spacing:2px;}
.maat-quote{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,28,13,0.9),rgba(26,21,9,0.9));border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1.2rem 1.4rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;border-left:3px solid var(--gold);}
.maat-quote p{font-style:italic;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7;}
.maat-quote span{display:block;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--gold-dim);margin-top:.5rem;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;}
.cards-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.9rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.card{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;text-align:center;}
.card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:var(--glow);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.card .icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;}
.card h3{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.2rem;}
.card p{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.pillars-section h2{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--gold-light);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.8rem;}
.pillar-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.8rem;padding:.7rem 1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;}
.pillar-icon{font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.pillar-text h4{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold);}
.pillar-text p{font-size:.73rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.chat-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:calc(100vh - 180px);}
.chat-msgs{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:.5rem 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.8rem;}
.msg{max-width:82%;padding:.85rem 1.1rem;border-radius:14px;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.6;animation:fadeUp .3s ease;}
.msg.tehuti{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,28,13,0.95),rgba(26,21,9,0.95));border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px 14px 14px 2px;align-self:flex-start;}
.msg.tehuti .msg-name{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.65rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.3rem;}
.msg.user{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal-dark),#155a56);border-radius:14px 14px 2px 14px;color:var(--white);align-self:flex-end;}
.chat-input-row{display:flex;gap:.6rem;padding:.8rem 0 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
.chat-input{flex:1;padding:.75rem 1rem;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;color:var(--text);font-size:.88rem;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;outline:none;resize:none;}
.chat-input:focus{border-color:var(--gold);}
.send-btn,.voice-btn{padding:.75rem 1rem;border-radius:10px;font-size:1.1rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;}
.voice-btn{border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--panel2);color:var(--gold);}
.send-btn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-dim));color:var(--deep);border:none;}
.voice-btn.recording{background:#8B2E2E;color:#fff;}
.reflection-day{text-align:center;padding:1rem 0;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--gold-dim);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.virtue-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1f1800,#0e0b02);border:1px solid var(--gold);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.virtue-card .v-symbol{font-size:2.8rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.virtue-card h2{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.virtue-card p{font-size:.87rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7;}
.affirmation-box{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1.1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.affirmation-box h3{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold-light);margin-bottom:.6rem;letter-spacing:2px;}
.affirmation-box p{font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.7;}
.checklist h3{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold-light);margin-bottom:.7rem;letter-spacing:2px;}
.check-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.8rem;padding:.6rem .8rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;}
.check-item.done{opacity:.6;border-color:var(--teal-dark);}
.check-item .cb{width:18px;height:18px;border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:.7rem;}
.check-item.done .cb{background:var(--teal-dark);border-color:var(--teal);}
.check-item span{font-size:.84rem;}
.new-entry-btn{width:100%;padding:.9rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-dim));color:var(--deep);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;border:none;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.journal-editor{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:.8rem;}
.journal-editor.open{display:flex;}
.j-input{width:100%;padding:.75rem 1rem;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;outline:none;}
.j-textarea{width:100%;min-height:160px;padding:.75rem 1rem;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;outline:none;resize:vertical;line-height:1.7;}
.j-row{display:flex;gap:.6rem;}
.j-save,.j-cancel{flex:1;padding:.7rem;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.8rem;cursor:pointer;border:none;}
.j-save{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-dim));color:var(--deep);}
.j-cancel{background:var(--panel2);color:var(--text-dim);border:1px solid var(--border);}
.journal-entry{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:.7rem;}
.je-date{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--gold-dim);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;margin-bottom:.3rem;}
.je-title{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--gold-light);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;margin-bottom:.2rem;}
.je-preview{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.report-header{text-align:center;padding:1rem 0;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.report-header h2{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);}
.report-header p{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;}
.report-section{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1.1rem;margin-bottom:.9rem;}
.report-section h3{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold-light);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.8rem;}
.virtue-bars{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.6rem;}
.v-bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;}
.v-bar-label{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim);width:70px;flex-shrink:0;}
.v-bar-track{flex:1;height:8px;background:var(--panel2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
.v-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--teal-dark),var(--gold));}
.v-bar-pct{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);width:32px;text-align:right;}
.mood-dots{display:flex;gap:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:.3rem;}
.mood-dot{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.95rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;}
.mood-dot.selected{border-color:var(--gold);transform:scale(1.15);}
.mood-label{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;text-align:center;}
.gen-report-btn{width:100%;padding:.9rem;margin-top:.5rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal-dark),#0d4a46);color:var(--white);font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;border:none;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;}
.ai-report-out{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--teal-dark);border-radius:12px;padding:1.1rem;margin-top:.9rem;display:none;font-size:.87rem;line-height:1.8;}
.ai-report-out.show{display:block;animation:fadeUp .5s ease;}
.sacred-space{text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0;}
.sacred-space h2{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.4rem;}
.sacred-space p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.breath-circle{width:140px;height:140px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--gold);margin:0 auto 1.2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.12);transition:all .3s;}
.breath-circle.inhale{animation:expand 4s ease-in-out forwards;}
.breath-circle.exhale{animation:contract 4s ease-in-out forwards;}
@keyframes expand{from{transform:scale(1);}to{transform:scale(1.3);}}
@keyframes contract{from{transform:scale(1.3);}to{transform:scale(1);}}
.breath-text{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--gold);}
.breath-phase{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:1rem;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;letter-spacing:2px;}
.smai-moves{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.7rem;margin-top:1rem;}
.move-card{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:.9rem;text-align:center;}
.move-card .m-icon{font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:.3rem;}
.move-card h4{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--gold);}
.move-card p{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.cal-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.cal-header h2{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--gold);}
.cal-nav{background:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:.3rem .7rem;color:var(--text-dim);cursor:pointer;}
.cal-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:.3rem;}
.cal-day-name{text-align:center;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--gold-dim);padding:.3rem 0;}
.cal-day{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim);cursor:pointer;}
.cal-day.today{background:var(--gold);color:var(--deep);font-weight:700;}
.cal-events{margin-top:1rem;}
.cal-events h3{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gold-light);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:.7rem;}
.event-item{display:flex;gap:.8rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:.7rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.event-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:.35rem;}
.event-text h4{font-size:.8rem;}
.event-text p{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.milestones-intro{text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.milestones-intro h2{font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:.3rem;}
.milestones-intro p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.milestone{display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center;padding:.9rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:.6rem;}
.milestone.achieved{border-color:var(--gold);background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,168,76,0.08),rgba(26,21,9,0.9));}
.ms-badge{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.3rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.milestone.achieved .ms-badge{border-color:var(--gold);}
.ms-info h4{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:.8rem;}
.milestone.achieved .ms-info h4{color:var(--gold);}
.ms-info p{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
.ms-check{margin-left:auto;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--gold);}
.spinner{display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-top-color:var(--gold);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .8s linear infinite;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--dark);}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--gold-dim);border-radius:3px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="stars"></div>
<div class="screen active" id="onboarding">
  <div class="onboard-box">
    <div class="ankh">☥</div>
    <div class="brand-title">Inner Compass<br/>Ma'at Rising</div>
    <div class="brand-sub">The Way of the Ma'atic Man</div>
    <hr class="divider"/>
    <div class="dot-row"><div class="dot active" id="d0"></div><div class="dot" id="d1"></div><div class="dot" id="d2"></div><div class="dot" id="d3"></div></div>
    <div class="step visible" id="step0"><div class="step-label">WELCOME, SEEKER</div><h2>Enter the Temple</h2><p>A sacred space for the African man walking the path of Ma'at — Truth, Justice, Balance, and Ancestral Wisdom. Tehuti-Mila walks beside you.</p><button class="ob-btn" onclick="nextStep(1)">Begin the Journey ☥</button></div>
    <div class="step" id="step1"><div class="step-label">YOUR IDENTITY</div><h2>What name do you carry?</h2><p>Enter the name by which the Ancestors shall know you.</p><input class="ob-input" id="ob-name" placeholder="Your name..." type="text"/><button class="ob-btn" onclick="nextStep(2)">Continue ☥</button></div>
    <div class="step" id="step2"><div class="step-label">YOUR LINEAGE</div><h2>Choose Your Spiritual Path</h2><p>Which ancestral tradition resonates most deeply?</p><select class="ob-input" id="ob-path"><option value="">— Select your path —</option><option>Kemetic / Ancient Egyptian</option><option>Yoruba / Ifá</option><option>Akan / Ashanti</option><option>Dogon</option><option>Pan-African Synthesis</option></select><button class="ob-btn" onclick="nextStep(3)">Continue ☥</button></div>
    <div class="step" id="step3"><div class="step-label">YOUR INTENTION</div><h2>What brings you to this temple?</h2><select class="ob-input" id="ob-intention"><option value="">— Choose your intention —</option><option>Spiritual Growth & Awakening</option><option>Inner Peace & Balance</option><option>Ancestral Connection</option><option>Purpose & Sacred Mission</option><option>Healing & Restoration</option></select><button class="ob-btn" onclick="completeOnboarding()">Enter the Temple ☥</button></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="screen" id="app">
  <div class="top-bar"><div class="top-title">☥ Ma'at Rising</div><div class="greeting-bar" id="greeting-bar">Welcome</div></div>
  <div class="tab-nav">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('temple',this)">🏛️ Temple</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('chat',this)">🔮 Tehuti-Mila</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('reflection',this)">☀️ Reflection</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('journal',this)">📜 Journal</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('report',this)">📊 Report</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('sacred',this)">🌬️ Sacred Space</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('calendar',this)">🗓️ Calendar</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('milestones',this)">🏆 Milestones</button>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-content active" id="tab-temple">
    <div class="temple-header"><span class="ankh-sm">☥</span><h1>Hall of Ma'at</h1><p id="temple-sub">The Path of the Balanced Man</p></div>
    <div class="maat-quote"><p id="wisdom-text">"The heart of a man is his own Neteru. Truth is the foundation upon which the eternal man stands."</p><span>— Ma'atic Wisdom</span></div>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card" onclick="switchTab('chat',null)"><div class="icon">🔮</div><h3>Tehuti-Mila</h3><p>Your AI Companion</p></div>
      <div class="card" onclick="switchTab('reflection',null)"><div class="icon">☀️</div><h3>Daily Reflection</h3><p>Today's Virtue</p></div>
      <div class="card" onclick="switchTab('journal',null)"><div class="icon">📜</div><h3>Sacred Scrolls</h3><p>Your Journal</p></div>
      <div class="card" onclick="switchTab('sacred',null)"><div class="icon">🌬️</div><h3>Sacred Breath</h3><p>Smai Tawi</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-section"><h2>THE 7 PILLARS OF THE MA'ATIC MAN</h2>
      <div class="pillar-item"><div class="pillar-icon">⚖️</div><div class="pillar-text"><h4>Ma'at — Truth & Justice</h4><p>Walk in alignment with cosmic law</p></div></div>
      <div class="pillar-item"><div class="pillar-icon">🦁</div><div class="pillar-text"><h4>Sekhem — Sacred Power</h4><p>Channel your divine masculine force</p></div></div>
      <div class="pillar-item"><div class="pillar-icon">👁️</div><div class="pillar-text"><h4>Medu — Sacred Word</h4><p>Speak only what you intend to create</p></div></div>
